        "category": "ancestryfeature",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your eyes are sharp, allowing you to make out small details about @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Concealed] or even @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Invisible] creatures that others might miss. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus when using the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Seek] action to find @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Hidden] or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Undetected] creatures within 30 feet of you. When you target an opponent that's concealed or hidden from you, reduce the DC of the flat check to 3 for a concealed target or to 9 for a hidden one.</p>"
